sis of CMB data from missions such as the MAP and the large scale\nstructure data from missions such as the DUET.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Apr 2002 21:10:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 6 Apr 2002 02:10:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
