 assumptions about the mass scales in the seesaw\nmechanism, the branching ratios of all lepton-flavor-changing processes are\nseveral orders of magnitude smaller than present experimental limits.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Apr 2002 10:04:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 7 Apr 2002 09:42:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
